{"tid":1444162,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［戰略討論］和理非快閃佔商場","createTime":"2019-08-11T11:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T11:57:24.000Z","uid":134248,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b0896d0fd953f5b081c4a00546bcddc97f0573be","tid":1444162,"uid":134248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:40:12.000Z","msg":"有見最近發夢人數一次畀一次少<br />\n狗拉既手足愈黎愈多。<br />\n而最重要係 手足佔路 塞鐵 黑警濫暴已經成為常態 政府繼續冷處理恐怕就會慢慢勝利<br />\n<br />\n所以我提議不如快閃佔商場 佔到落閘就轉場<br />\n轉去邊就臨場討論 務求加大影響 迫商家落場"},{"pid":"cb51c9d269c54edd85e1cf077b53f8fcdafd12bb","tid":1444162,"uid":134248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:40:45.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1f967e575ca99c21122e54edd1572cab9b2508a0","tid":1444162,"uid":134248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451e7e3ee05f9ef1d41e010682866c928e37a3d7","tid":1444162,"uid":134248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:41:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2fcbb0b1fb7625466e0c9d573bceae03ffccab","tid":1444162,"uid":134248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28800ffa373a892ae34778a6fabb8263fbb1bae7","tid":1444162,"uid":134248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d369f6f548883c587238e38b94959923cc0284a","tid":1444162,"uid":134248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e6989a230c1ab8f9e2150cd1f7a3fc28905b80","tid":1444162,"uid":134248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:42:00.000Z","